<!DOCTYPE  html>
<html lang="es">
    <Head>
        <title>This is a TITLE inside a HEAD</title>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,  initial-scale=1.0">
        /*For media queries we add within the STYLE tag the queries to define the style of the objects inside the page*/

        <style>
            @media (min-width: 601px){/*size of 601px or bigger*/
                body {
                    background-color: burlywood;
                }
            }

            @media (max-width: 600px){/* size of 600px or smaller*/
                body {
                    background-color: cornflowerblue;
                }
            }
        </style>



    </Head>
    <body>
        <h1>This is an H1 tag nested in a BODY tag</h1>
        <h6>This is an H6 tag which is the smallest heading on HTML</h6>

        Ordered list:
        <ol>
            <li>one item</li>
            <li>another item</li>
            <li>third item</li>
        </ol>

        Unordered list:
        <ul>
            <li>one item</li>
            <li>another item</li>
            <li>another item, no matter which one since it is an unordered list</li>
        </ul>

        This is an image tag, image tag is self closing it doesn't need a closing tag

        <img src="Millennium-Falcon.jpg" width="500"> <!-- This tag is self closing -->

        This is an a (anchor) tag
        <a href="https://static3.srcdn.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Millennium-Falcon.jpg"> Millenium falcon image on internet</a>


        This is a table done by code on HTML
        <!-- Here is where the table starts, father tag is TABLE, then THEAD and TBODY then TH and TD respectively -->
        <table>
            <thead>
                <th>Column one header</th>
                <th>Column two header</th>
                <th>Column three header</th>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>1st Col 1st R</td>
                    <td>2nd Col 1st R</td>
                    <td>3rd Col 1st R</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>1st Col 2nd R</td>
                    <td>2nd Col 2nd R</td>
                    <td>3rd Col 2nd R</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <!-- This is where the TABLE ends -->

        Form
        <form>

            <div>
                <input type="text" placeholder="This is what user sees before filling with text" name="_variable_name">
                <input type="submit">
            </div>

            <div>
                <input type="password" name="_passw_var" placeholder="passw please">
            </div>

            <div>
                Favourite color?
                <input type="radio" name="_selected_color" value="red"> Red
                <input type="radio" name="_selected_color" value="blue"> Blue
            </div>

            <div>
                <input name="country" list="countries" placeholder="Select Country">
                <datalist id="countries">
                    <option value="Af">
                    <option value="Af1">
                    <option value="Af2">
                    <option value="B">
                    <option value="C">
                </datalist>
            </div>
            
        </form>


    </body>

</html>